fullDescription.text: Checks for versions with CSRF token forgery vulnerability (CVE-2020-8166).
Checks for unsafe deserialization of objects.
Finds instances of possible command injection.
Check if HTML escaping is disabled for JSON output.
Warn on potentially dangerous attributes allowed via permit.
Check for unsafe use of Object#send.
Check for user input in uses of send_file.
Checks for session key length and http_only settings.
Checks for session key length and http_only settings.
Checks for unescaped output in views.
Report uses of validates_format_of with improper anchors.
